AGI - Scene changes in front of the gip: the 35-year-old mechanic of Cianciana, arrested on the charge of having tried to <a href="https://www.agi.it/cronaca/news/2024-05-23/uomo-accoltella-moglie-agrigentino-26502939/"> killing his wife and children of 6 and 3 years The interrogation, in front of the Sciacca court gip, Antonino Cucinella, lasted a few minutes. The investigator, assisted by his lawyers Maurizio Gaudio and Luca Burgio, informed the intention not to answer questions and the hearing ended. In the coming hours, the judge's decision will be awaited on the request for validation and application of the precautionary custody of the public prosecutor Brunella Fava. The man would have angered with unheardened ferocity.
&nbsp;
The <a href="https://www.agi.it/cronaca/news/2024-05-24/bambini-accoltellati-da-padre-agrigento- come-stanno-26517503/">conditions of the two children </a>, meanwhile, remain very serious even if the small 6 years is improving. The child suffered two interventions: one in the chest, which affected a lung and also the heart, and one in neurosurgery to the brain. The little sister has several injuries to her face, two very deep concern the doctors. The wife has less serious injuries and her conditions do not cause concern. The man, after the woman had managed to escape carrying her son, handed over the child and barricaded in the house for almost six hours and then arrested by the carabinieri after a very long mediation.
&nbsp;
The military, coordinated by the Sciacca Prosecutor, interviewed neighbors and acquaintances of the couple to try to make full light on the mad aggression that, according to a first investigative hypothesis, would have originated from the announced will of the woman to separate.&nbsp;

